This statistics report contains amapping of statistic category string names to objects containing the corresponding statistics data.

Calling getStats() on an lets you specify whether you wish to obtain statistics for outbound, inbound, or all streams on the connection. The and versions of getStats() specifically only return statistics available to the incoming or outgoing stream on which you call them.
